Celestial Tracker		KEY:Celestial Tracker ~ AngelBlooded	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.AngelBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Celestial Tracker ~ AngelBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]		PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Angel-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Angel-Blooded]			DESC:You share the same talent for tracking evildoers that your angelic ancestor possessed. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Survival checks made to follow tracks. In addition, you treat trails as being up to 24 hours fresher than they actually are when using the Survival skill to follow tracks.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.21		BONUS:SKILL|Survival (Follow tracks)|1
Planetar's Visions	KEY:Planetar's Visions ~ AngelBlooded	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.AngelBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Planetar's Visions ~ AngelBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]		PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Angel-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Angel-Blooded]			DESC:Ever since you were a child, you've experienced vivid dreams of cutting down hordes of shrieking, twisted Azatas. Whenever you succeed at a critical hit with a melee weapon against an evil outsider, you ignore an amount of the outsider's damage reduction (if any) equal to the critical multiplier of your weapon (this cannot reduce a creature's damage reduction to below 0).								SOURCEPAGE:p.21
