Good Influence		KEY:Good Influence ~ ArchonBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.ArchonBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Good Influence ~ ArchonBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]		PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Archon-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Archon-Blooded]		DESC:You possess an innate ability to motivate and inspire others to do the right thing. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks when attempting to persuade a nongood creature to make a decision that benefits the cause of good, and when persuading a nonlawful creature to make a decision in line with the laws of the region. These bonuses stack if you attempt to persuade a nongood, nonlawful creature to take a lawful good action.	SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Lantern Spirit		KEY:Lantern Spirit ~ ArchonBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.ArchonBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Lantern Spirit ~ ArchonBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]		PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Archon-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Archon-Blooded]		DESC:Your celestial ancestor was a lantern archon for centuries before ascending to a higher rank. You feel a strange sense of nostalgia whenever you use your continual flame spell-like ability, and can use it as a move action instead of a standard action.																							SOURCEPAGE:p.22
