Bralani's Step		KEY:Bralani's Step ~ AzataBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.AzataBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Bralani's Step ~ AzataBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Azata-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Azata-Blooded]			DESC:Your ancestor was a bralani, an azata known for its untamed speed in battle. When in combat, you feel a fierce surge of energy through your limbs. Once per day, you may move an additional s feet as part of a move action.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Lillend's Harp		KEY:Lillend's Harp ~ AzataBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.AzataBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Lillend's Harp ~ AzataBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Azata-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Azata-Blooded]			DESC:Your ancestor was a lillend, a being of exceptional grace and singular musical talent. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Perform (string) checks. This bonus increases to +2 when you make a Perform check as part of a bardic performance. 																										SOURCEPAGE:p.22		BONUS:SKILL|Perform (String Instruments)|1
