Snake Hater			KEY:Snake Hater ~ GarudaBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.GarudaBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Snake Hater ~ GarudaBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Garuda-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Garuda-Blooded]		DESC:You've always loathed serpents and other slithering monsters, ever since you can remember, and have studied them extensively. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Knowledge (dungeoneering) checks and Knowledge (dungeoneering) is always a class skill for you.																								SOURCEPAGE:p.23		BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Dungeoneering)|2|TYPE=Trait		CSKILL:Knowledge (Dungeoneering)
Toxophilite			KEY:Toxophilite ~ GarudaBlooded		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait.AasimarRaceTrait.GarudaBloodedRaceTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Toxophilite ~ GarudaBlooded],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait]			PREMULT:1,[PRETEMPLATE:1,Aasimar (Garuda-Blooded)],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Adoptive Race ~ Aasimar Garuda-Blooded]		DESC:You've inherited some of your celestial ancestor's prowess with the bow, and gain a +2 trait bonus on attack rolls made to confirm critical hits with bows.																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.23
